ily:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;border-style:initial;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:578px;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;height:65px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be35e013&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uosEWwB4iaKPdBBHJlD4GYRHOytPia6moa4MPQDibjKXtvUvts27RcWa5OQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fqkp9c1rkrfw0xnwl\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <h2 style=\"padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌让AI打出丝滑连招：编码-部署-自测-改bug</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&amp;mid=2650541895&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=6f5f8af100dba54c4675b2c2db62e416&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kXkKTLMMTcJSpBE3bQiEFg\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kXkKTLMMTcJSpBE3bQiEFg</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文提出了一种测试驱动的AI编程闭环工作流，旨在解决AI辅助编程中“最后一公里”的问题——即AI生成代码后缺乏自测与迭代能力。通过引入自动化验收和反馈机制，构建了包含编码、部署、自测、改Bug的完整闭环。文章以“收藏夹功能修复”为例，验证了该工作流的有效性，证明只要提供清晰的需求、技术方案和测试用例，AI就能像合格程序员一样完成自我修复与持续优化，未来还可通过增强测试、诊断、任务拆分等能力进一步提升自动化水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968279\" width=\"1000\" data-type=\"other\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=00253f8f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TQXn8madcZYvrOpQ86kYjgtwfSnkRSOwzA4RM6epIwS5TfPXCF5Ewdu6UCCgMEca5ygZwiaQAqeIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌从0到1：天猫AI测试用例生成的实践与突破</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&amp;mid=2650541896&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=55fb4c42cda750d35e32b1b5c8d573ea&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XTKbyk0ZHYYdpY5Hvn4PLw\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XTKbyk0ZHYYdpY5Hvn4PLw</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文系统介绍天猫技术团队在 AI 赋能测试领域的深度实践，聚焦通过差异化用例生成功能，结合标准化需求、知识库（RAG）与平台化集成，提升用例覆盖率与效率，同时探索将QA从“体力劳动”转向“脑力劳动”的转型路线，以实现更高覆盖率、更快速度和更低成本的质量保障。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968278\" width=\"495\" data-type=\"other\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0596c74d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TQXn8madcZYvrOpQ86kYjgibVHpAKEF6OWoEU8NHuDD0DlCLOPj0pnUvOhLvWwl6Nq3cNQ0jVcjPg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌得物TiDB升级实践</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&amp;mid=2247541552&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ed3e6d033bdc80f369f008feafbb6691&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/cPMI0oEW3iHK-0l149X87g\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/cPMI0oEW3iHK-0l149X87g</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">得物DBA自2020年初开始自建TiDB，5年以来随着NewSQL数据库迭代发展、运维体系逐步完善、产品自身能力逐步提升，接入业务涵盖了多个业务线和关键场景。从第一套TIDB v4.0.9 版本开始，到后来v4.0.11、v5.1.1、v5.3.0，在经历了各种 BUG 踩坑、问题调试后，最终稳定在 TIDB 5.3.3 版本。伴随着业务高速增长、数据量逐步增多，对 TiDB 的稳定性及性能也带来更多挑战和新的问题。为了应对这些问题，DBA团队决定对 TiDB 进行一次版本升级，收敛版本到7.5.x。本文基于内部的实践情况，从架构、新特性、升级方案及收益等几个方向讲述 TiDB 的升级之旅。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968280\" width=\"906\" data-type=\"other\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d7c486c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TQXn8madcZYvrOpQ86kYjgpjxJ0xnA9qoq3WiaH5BjzWlRMJnKicbSu8ZVUQSAEGoaHBQrGkzsHnNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌关于智能体（AI Agent）搭建，Dify、n8n、Coze 超详细的总结！</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyNjM2MzQyNg==&amp;mid=2247715041&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=855940f5de5135807cfdf70f09f9fc89&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7QvVGC1GzAfTMQPwmbYx-A\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7QvVGC1GzAfTMQPwmbYx-A</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文系统梳理了以低代码平台搭建智能体（AI Agent）的理念、方法与实操要点，比较了 Dify、n8n 与 Coze 三大平台的定位、优劣和适用场景，并提出“混合开发”的选型思路，强调平台化能够降低门槛、提升效率与可观测性，同时保持对底层代码的灵活掌控。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968282\" width=\"1080\" data-type=\"other\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=16fa91fc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TQXn8madcZYvrOpQ86kYjgl2EInTLADMpTwCibHvTmTBH9xZRuuibEh9iaJp2cGyxY9H7v0nx7eQZow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌图解：101个支付名词</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDIwNjAxMA==&amp;mid=2247489243&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1249864d120249e9f78b7b6eac730a64&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Z6rrPcv48zSSd5peUGGRDA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Z6rrPcv48zSSd5peUGGRDA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文以图解的形式系统梳理支付领域的101个名词，涵盖支付的三大核心过程（交易、清算、结算）及其衍生的交易、余额、产品名称、客户名词、通道/网关/渠道、会计名词、结算名词、账务系统、风险与安全等维度，旨在帮助读者通过直观图示理解复杂的支付术语及其相互关系，并鼓励读者补充更多名词。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968281\" width=\"810\" data-type=\"other\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a2913f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2TQXn8madcZYvrOpQ86kYjgaknCJwcuWp4EmjjXIPANKKfWXF05IKiaQxvzE9eJhCLG34v3FMrSib5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌【文章翻译】Cursor 内部观察</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwOTMzMzk0MQ==&amp;mid=2247498276&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0f181e8e17a3464ec3e66416a8941aeb&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/rys1k0BEg3Xqw6iPCWzKmw\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/rys1k0BEg3Xqw6iPCWzKmw</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本篇记录整理了对 AI 编程公司 Cursor 的六十天观察，聚焦其极致的线下协作文化、高水平的招聘与自用驱动产品开发，以及由创始人带动的天花板思维与成熟的团队气质，展现了一家以自驱与高参与度为核心的高密度人才生态及“使命即奖赏”的工作哲学。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"margin: 24px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 48px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 65px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6cd7e58&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoVw3ibDBtUOIklnu30LHYQBArbGTZwnwokZzibw3DIeVlsscsP5PcbC3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fqkp9c1rkrfw0xnwl\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  </h2>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌Microverse：一个模拟上帝类的沙盒游戏</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/KsanaDock/Microverse\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/KsanaDock/Microverse</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个上帝模拟沙盒游戏建立在Godot 4作为一个多智能体人工智能社会模拟系统。在这个虚拟世界中，人工智能角色拥有独立的思维和记忆，能够进行自主的社会互动，完成任务，并通过持续的交流发展复杂的社会关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:48px 8px 0em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;height: 65px;width: 578px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d8a4b282&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoQrLTibmRJELUQysO80354ouUOACwWDCCr0NXNjicZbicDGqrqvPSHdibicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:justify;\"><ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fqkp9c1rkrfw0xnwl\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌【最全版】段永平退休20多年后罕见公开访谈！方略对聊个人经历、企业经营、投资理念、公司理解等...2万字收藏！</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MjE3ODgzNA==&amp;mid=2652383563&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1d09c9437a6d3bc81e24dca47a395397&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/YDxnuKVKmEOlPCu2DWg6Aw\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/YDxnuKVKmEOlPCu2DWg6Aw</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文整理了段永平在《方略》节目中的长时对话，系统回顾他的个人成长、企业治理、投资理念、对苹果与茅台等优质标的的判断，以及对教育和AI等前沿议题的观点，呈现他“买股票就是买公司”的核心投资逻辑、对企业文化与边界清单的坚持，以及在复杂环境中通过授权、选人和长期耐心实现可持续成长的思考。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"hack\" data-id=\"hack\">\n    <div data-support=\"96编辑器\" data-style-id=\"31634\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n       <div style=\"width: 20%;color: rgb(119, 175, 81);font-size: 20px;margin-bottom: 12px;\" data-width=\"20%\">\n        <div style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n         <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">END</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
